Class BaseTEntityChangesBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.beans.base.BaseTEntityChangesBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TEntityChangesBean

    public abstract class BaseTEntityChangesBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This table holds the changed entities for updating the full text search index in each clusternode You should not use this class directly. It should not even be extended; all references should be to TEntityChangesBean
